(17031, 4986, 0, 2, '【大提琴的告白】', '你是用什麼樣的方式去愛著一個人??\r\n\r\n又或者\r\n\r\n妳可知道...\r\n\r\n有一個人 這樣愛著妳..??\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n大提琴的音色\r\n\r\n溫厚飽滿 沉默孤獨\r\n\r\n卻有一股安全感\r\n\r\n是我選用來詮釋\r\n\r\n一個永遠站在身邊\r\n\r\n默默為她付出的那個"他"\r\n\r\n最貼切的聲音....\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n曲子從開始到第一段都由鋼琴獨奏\r\n\r\n在我的畫面中\r\n\r\n是代表一個清澈的動人的女孩\r\n\r\n娓娓的唱著自己\r\n\r\n至於唱些什麼??\r\n\r\n我也不知\r\n\r\n也許是期待愛吧....\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n到了曲中轉調處\r\n\r\n在一旁等待許久的他\r\n\r\n忍不住終於唱出口了\r\n\r\n把自己心中諸多的壓抑情感\r\n\r\n一一的訴說了出來.......\r\n\r\n這份訴說是不計後果也不求期待的\r\n\r\n因為這輩子\r\n\r\n不管發生什麼事\r\n\r\n他永遠都會願意\r\n\r\n默默的為她付出\r\n\r\n當一個無形的肩膀.......\r\n', '2009-02-12 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 2, 4, '', '', 243, '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2009-04-06 23:35:58', '2013-10-07 17:14:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(17032, 12367, 0, 1, 'Destination', '', '2010-02-26 00:00:00', 0000, 20, 0, 7, 'Once I tried and tried for this goal\r\nI did \r\nBut I gave up, I screwed up\r\nWhen the night came crushing it all\r\nWill you be there\r\nPlease help me, if you can\r\nI have to try and try for this goal\r\nSomeday\r\nI still hope, I still long\r\nWill the suspense keep what it said\r\nSomeday\r\nThe pain will, disappear\r\n\r\nSay I, that I love you\r\nI can’t live without you, tonight\r\nSay I, that I love you\r\nI can’t breathe without you, tonight\r\n\r\nOnce I tried and tried for this goal\r\nI failed\r\nI felt lost, in this world\r\nBut I think I meet the best dream now\r\nYou’re there\r\nPlease don’t leave, for awhile\r\nI have to try and try for this goal\r\nCause I know\r\nIt’s quite near, it’s right there\r\nCan you hear me cry out this plea\r\nIf you can\r\nJust give me, a sign now\r\n\r\nI’ll find the destination, it’s not so far\r\nCan you come with me? Just tonight (Just you and I tonight)', '', 199, '', '振中', '振中', '振中', '', '', 1, 0, 0, '2009-04-07 00:08:19', '2015-03-12 13:39:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
