(17038, 12367, 0, 1, 'A Letter To You', '', '2010-02-26 00:00:00', 0000, 20, 0, 7, 'The sunlight comes in, the birds are singing\r\nJust let it go, let the morning begin\r\nEverything seems to be so serene\r\nBut why do you still fell upset\r\n\r\nIt’s so sad that you couldn’t get rid of these shitty things\r\nIt’s so sad that you lock yourself in the narrow cage\r\n\r\nYou have to look at the world and, then look at yourself \r\nJust open your hands and see what is in\r\nI’m sure that, you’ll find your smile again\r\n\r\nYou can feel the winds, you can touch the rain\r\nSo forget the scars, and remember the laugh\r\nWell after all things can’t be that bad\r\nJust because you fear to get through\r\n\r\n', '', 185, '', '振中', '振中', '振中', '', '', 1, 0, 0, '2009-04-07 11:10:13', '2015-03-12 13:39:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(17039, 12367, 0, 1, '停留', '', '2010-02-26 00:00:00', 0000, 20, 0, 7, '背著過去的包袱 我慢慢向前走\r\n到底什麼時候 才能學會知足\r\n我張開了手 卻撲了個空\r\n好想停留 在快樂的時候\r\n一陣風 叫醒我\r\n\r\n以為已做的夠多 但總還差一些\r\n也許幸運女神 能再給些眷戀\r\n我張開了手 卻撲了個空\r\n好想停留 在單純的時候\r\n一陣風 叫醒我\r\n\r\n好想停留 在作夢的時候\r\n好想停留 在作夢的時候\r\n請別再叫醒我 請別再叫醒我\r\n', '', 192, '', '振中', '振中', '振中', '', '', 1, 0, 0, '2009-04-07 11:25:32', '2015-03-12 13:39:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(17040, 12367, 0, 1, 'I''m Leaving', '', '2010-02-26 00:00:00', 0000, 20, 0, 7, 'the day we met\r\nthe place we met\r\nall those things were just like wind\r\nthey blewed, we walk\r\nI saw you smile\r\nI heard you laugh\r\nbring those memories \r\nit''s time to move on\r\n\r\ni''m leaving, please don''t cry for me\r\ni''m just another person, in your story\r\nhey i''m leaving, please don''t cry for me\r\nyour new life is just coming around \r\n\r\nwe lit up the candle \r\nnot for staying all night\r\nbut for finding the road\r\ndon''t feel sad\r\ndon''t look back\r\nbring those memory\r\nit''s time to move on\r\n\r\ni''m leaving, please don''t cry for me\r\ni''m just another person, in your story\r\nhey i''m leaving, please don''t cry for me\r\nit''s just the time to find the ways to way\r\n\r\n', '', 193, '', '振中', '振中', '振中', '', '', 1, 0, 0, '2009-04-07 12:40:15', '2015-03-12 13:39:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(17041, 2307, 1802, 14, 'New Born', '', '2006-06-01 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 7, '', '\nI''m the songbird flying from tree to tree\n\nI''m the cloud that hangs on the sky and floats away\n\nI''m the zephyr breezing tenderly\n\nI''m the flower that blooms wildly on the grass\n\n\nI''m the blaze in the dark\n\nI''m star that brightens the night\n\nAnd shines alight\n\nI''m so exited\n\nI feel like I''m a newborn child\n\n\nEverything is just so fine\n\nKiss me lovely and hold me tight\n\nNothing’s better than this brand new period of time\n\nBut I''m a little afraid of that is coming to me\n\nAround me', 325, '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2008-06-17 21:36:01', '2015-03-12 13:39:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(17042, 10064, 1802, 15, '就這樣', '', '2009-02-17 00:33:46', 0000, 0, 1, 10, '在這個普通的下午，沒有上課也沒有出門，沒有咖啡有我也不加糖\r\n今天就是要忙著無聊\r\n看看手背上記下的事，沒有一件事我有做到\r\n這算不算失敗，我不知道不知道不知道\r\n\r\n我在想我會不會　　就這樣　到最後\r\n沒幾根毛卻一堆煩惱\r\n就這樣　到最後　　才幾歲我就開始養老\r\n\r\n那些十幾年的老朋友，沒有一個會打給我，最近過的怎麼樣，\r\n有些事也想跟你講\r\nI dont know why　今天就是有一點而怪怪\r\n站起來　我不知道不知道不知道\r\n\r\n我走到廚房去到了一杯水，想到要出門但又忘了要去找誰，\r\n我想了五分鐘算了我決定我要再來喝一杯\r\n再來躺回去床上繼續著我的煩惱\r\n', '', 135, '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2009-02-17 00:33:46', '2015-03-12 13:39:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(17043, 12297, 1802, 16, 'free Burma', '金箔的黃金佛塔，紅袈裟的和尚，飄揚的沙龍，梵音繚繞的佛國。帝國之眼下浪漫的異域，矇住了許多的眼睛，看不見的，是群群被貼上第三世界標籤的難民和無止境的災害，以及強權迫害下的民主自由。free Burma，free the way。世界上的他者，也是本我的縮影碎片。free Burma and Aung San Suu Kyi。同翁山蘇姬一起前進。\r\n', '2009-04-04 00:00:00', 0000, 0, 1, 5, 'Free Burma（自由緬甸）\r\n\r\n\r\n依是米鄉ㄟ國度，本是有依靠\r\n軍人自私ㄟ執政，阻礙民主ㄟ去路，\r\n為了民主ㄟ奮鬥，恁卻來犧牲\r\n就算生命受威脅，意志卻是更堅強\r\n\r\nfree Burma～free the way ～\r\nfree Burma～free the way～\r\n\r\n無法生存ㄟ環境，只好來流浪\r\n泰緬邊境ㄟ難民，世界孤兒在祈禱，\r\n甘是天公伯考驗，風颱來戲弄\r\n折磨心情誰知影，還有一段路要走\r\n\r\nfree Burma～free the way ～\r\nfree Burma～free the way～\r\nfree Burma～free the way ～\r\nfree Burma and Aung San Suu Kyi ～\r\n', '', 215, '', '老諾', '老諾', '', 'Gamaa Music', '', 1, 1, 0, '2009-04-04 00:34:55', '2015-03-12 13:39:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
